cdata.name: HoboNickels
cdata.desc: HoboNickels (HBN) is an extremely fast and efficient crypto-currency based on bottlecaps - (CAPS). With a Proof of Work block time of 30 seconds and 5 coins per block. There is a 2% super stake every 10 days - so 100% a year of holding your coins in your wallet - the opposite principle to Freicoin and its demurrage fee.
